{"type":"message","id":"f8305a4c","parentId":"db890f34","timestamp":"2026-03-17T16:03:09.722Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"process:5","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"          |\n|           |                                     | 助有需要的技术用户更实时、简洁、轻量的使用相  |                    |\n|           |                                     | 关数据。                                      |                    |\n+-----------+-------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+--------------------+\n\nTip: use `npx clawhub` to search, install, and sync skills.\n[plugins] plugins.allow is empty; discovered non-bundled plugins may auto-load: openclaw-lark (C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\extensions\\openclaw-lark\\index.js). Set plugins.allow to explicit trusted ids.\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes\n[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool\n[plugins] feishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools\n[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_user_message, feishu_im_user_fetch_resource, feishu_im_user_get_messages, feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages, feishu_im_user_search_messages\n[plugins] feishu_search: Registered feishu_search_doc_wiki\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive_file, feishu_doc_comments, feishu_doc_media\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki_space, feishu_wiki_space_node\n[plugins] feishu_sheets: Registered feishu_sheet tool\n[plugins] feishu_im_bot_image: Registered feishu_im_bot_image tool\n[plugins] feishu_im: Registered feishu_im_bot_image\n[plugins] Registered all OAPI tools (calendar, task, bitable, search, drive, wiki, sheets, im)\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_fetch_doc, feishu_create_doc, feishu_update_doc\n[plugins] feishu_oauth: Registered feishu_oauth tool\n[plugins] feishu_oauth_batch_auth: Registered feishu_oauth_batch_auth tool\n[plugins] openclaw-lark: loaded without install/load-path provenance; treat as untracked local code and pin trust via plugins.allow or install records (C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\extensions\\openclaw-lark\\index.js)\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"calm-falcon","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Skills (33/77 ready)\n+-----------+-------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+--------------------+\n| Status    | Skill                               | Description                                   | Source             |\n+-----------+-------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------------+--------------------+\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-doc                       | Feishu document read/write operations.        | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | Activate when user mentions Feishu docs,      |                    |\n|           |                                     | cloud docs, or docx links.                    |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-drive                     | Feishu cloud storage file management.         | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | Activate when user mentions cloud space,      |                    |\n|           |                                     | folders, drive.                               |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-perm                      | Feishu permission management for documents    | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | and files. Activate when user mentions        |                    |\n|           |                                     | sharing, permissions, collaborators.          |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-wiki                      | Feishu knowledge base navigation. Activate    | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | when user mentions knowledge base, wiki, or   |                    |\n|           |                                     | wiki links.                                   |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-bitable                   | 飞书多维表格（Bitable）的创建、查询、编辑和管 | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | 理工具。包含 27                               |                    |\n|           |                                     | 种字段类型支持、高级筛选、批量操作和视图管理  |                    |\n|           |                                     | 。                                            |                    |\n|           |                                     | **当以下情况时使用此 Skill**：                |                    |\n|           |                                     | (1) 需要创建或管理飞书多维表格 App            |                    |\n|           |                                     | (2)                                           |                    |\n|           |                                     | 需要在多维表格中新增、查询、修改、删除记录（  |                    |\n|           |                                     | 行数据）                                      |                    |\n|           |                                     | (3) 需要管理字段（列）、视图、数据表          |                    |\n|           |                                     | (4)                                           |                    |\n|           |                                     | 用户提到\"多维表格\"、\"bitable\"、\"数据表\"、\"记  |                    |\n|           |                                     | 录\"、\"字段\"                                   |                    |\n|           |                                     | (5) 需要批量导入数据或批量更新多维表格        |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-calendar                  | 飞书日历与日程管理工具集。包含日历管理、日程  | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | 管理、参会人管理、忙闲查询。                  |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-channel-rules             | Lark/Feishu channel output rules. Always      | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | active in Lark conversations.                 |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-create-doc                | 创建飞书云文档。从 Lark-flavored Markdown     | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | 内容创建新的飞书云文档，支持指定创建位置（文  |                    |\n|           |                                     | 件夹/知识库/知识空间）。                      |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-fetch-doc                 | 获取飞书云文档内容。返回文档的 Markdown       | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | 内容，支持处理文档中的图片、文件和画板（需配  |                    |\n|           |                                     | 合 feishu_doc_media 工具）。                  |                    |\n| ✓ ready   | 📦 feishu-im-read                   | 飞书 IM                                       | openclaw-extra     |\n|           |                                     | 消息读取工具使用指南，覆盖会话消息获取、话题  |                    |\n|           |                                     | 回复读取、跨会话消息搜索、图片/文件资源下载。 |                    |\n|           |                                     | **当以下情况时使用此 Skill**:                 |                    |\n|           |                                     | (1) 需要获取群聊或单聊的历史消息              |                    |\n|           |                                     | (2) 需要读取话题（thread）内的回复消息        |                    |\n|           |                                     | (3)                                           |                    |\n|           |                                     | 需要跨会话搜索消息（按关键词、发送者、时间等  |                    |\n|           |                                     | 条件）                                        |                    |\n|           |                                     | (4)                                           |                    |\n|           |  